WEBVTT

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:03.680
So, I don't like to boast,

00:00:03.719 --> 00:00:09.256
but I am very good at finding things
to be annoyed about.

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:11.376
It is a real specialty of mine.

00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:15.296
I can hear 100 compliments
and a single insult,

00:00:15.320 --> 00:00:16.816
and what do I remember?

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:18.216
The insult.

00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:20.936
And according to
the research, I'm not alone.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:26.496
Unfortunately, the human brain
is wired to focus on the negative.

00:00:26.520 --> 00:00:29.856
Now, this might have been helpful
when we were cave people,

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:31.736
trying to avoid predators,